    <title>Íµ¨Îß§ ÏöîÏ≤≠ ÏÉÅÏÑ∏</title>
    <style>
        /* Ï†ÑÏ≤¥ Ïä§ÌÉÄÏùº Î¶¨ÏÖã */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }

        .container {
